    Class template of CarMaker holds the behaviour and attributes of the carMaker class which are required for the assignment. It has a paramterized and a default constructor. Class sets and gets different field values such as reigistration number, year Made, car Colour etc. Setters and getters methods are used for the purpose of providing possible information about a single car object.
